---
title: Miso Honey Hake in Coconut Curry with mushrooms and jasmine rice
description: Packed with B vitamins and plenty of protein, hake is a great source of nutrients. Not only is this dinner nourishing, it's also filling, fragrant, and flavourful to the max.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W20_IE_IECF20237-3_Main_high-0b130877.jpg
